    </statement>
  </exercise>

  <exercise>
    <title>High School and Beyond, mathematical interval</title>
    <statement>
      <p>We considered the differences between the reading and writing scores of a random sample of 200 students who took the High School and Beyond Survey. The mean and standard deviation of the differences are <m>\bar{x}_{read-write} = -0.545</m> and <m>s_{read-write} = 8.887</m> points.</p>
